Double click and run the script file IDLDE_as_root prior to running any code. This will ensure that all code is run as a sudo (super admin)
Double click setup.sh if there are errors due to missing installation files

car6.py

- ensure that the cannon is connected to the USB first prior to running the code. Otherwise there will be an error.
- car6.py - controls the car and the cannon

ultrasonicsensortest.py
- This tests the ultrasonic sensor and the temperature / humidity sensor 
- There is no need to connect the cannon for this one.
- Connect the Ultrasonic sensor to D2 and the temperature sensor to D4
